                    üè† Dashboard
                </a>
                <a href="/games" class="nav-link px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-10" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    üéÆ Games
                </a>
                <a href="/quiz" class="nav-link px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-10" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
